                            <comment id="27383" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Wed, 7 Nov 2007 05:21:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We unfortunately can&apos;t change the present behavior easily. If those semantics don&apos;t work for you, then you&apos;ll need to use some other mechanism, not implementing ApplicationListener...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&apos;ll revisit the ApplicationListener model for Spring 3.0.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
